comment: Griffin (LAC) sets the screen on Rubio (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Redick (LAC) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with LaVine (MIN) that does not affect his drive and shot attempt.

Rubio (MIN) makes incidental contact with Griffin's (LAC) arm that does not affect his layup attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Wiggins (MIN) was upheld. Los Angeles was awarded possession.

Jordan (LAC) makes contact with Rubio's (MIN) body that affects his shot attempt.
Griffin (LAC) sets the screen on Wiggins (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
